server.c & client.c:
    A simple illustration of how socket programming works, client
    set server messages and server print the message out.

NBserver.c & NBclient.c:
    These 2 show why we need to transfer to network byte ordering for
    transferring data.

getHostByName.c getHostByAddr.c getPeerName.c getHostName.c:
    Just for showing the usage of 4 functions.
